    <header>
      {{> navbar}}

      <div
        class="container-fluid bg"
        style="
          background-image: url('images/grandCanyonPose.jpg');
          background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
          background-size: cover;
          background-position: center;
          height: 100vh;
          background-blend-mode: darken;
        "
      >
        <div
          class="d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center h-100 text-center text-white"
        >
          <h1 class="display-2">Keegan Churchill</h1>
          <h2 class="display-6">
            <b>Welcome to my webpage</b>
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="container col-xxl-10 px-4 py-5">
        <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center">
          <div class="d-none d-lg-flex col-lg-6">
            <img
              src="images/grandCanyonCaveWaterfall.jpg"
              class="d-block rounded img-fluid mx-auto"
              alt="Keegan navigating a waterfall inside a grotto"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-3">
              About Me
            </h1>
            <p class="lead">
              Hi, I’m Keegan Churchill — a computer scientist based in Mount
              Pearl, Newfoundland, with a passion for designing smart and
              efficient systems. My journey into programming began in high
              school, where I was amazed by how a few well-written instructions
              could bring computers to life. My love for video games and
              problem-solving led me to merge these worlds, culminating in one
              of my proudest achievements: developing a
              <a
                class="link-body-emphasis"
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/StarCraft"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                >StarCraft</a
              >
              :
              <a
                class="link-body-emphasis"
                href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/StarCraft:_Brood_War"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                >Brood War</a
              >
              bot using
              <a
                class="link-body-emphasis"
                href="https://bwapi.github.io/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener"
                >BWAPI</a
              >
              . Watching projects incrementally improve, iterating toward
              efficiency and success, is something I find deeply satisfying.
              Whether it’s AI, game development, or solving real-world problems,
              I thrive on turning ideas into impactful solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container px-4 mt-5">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">JOBS!</h2>
        <div class="d-md-none">
          {{#jobs}}
          <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">
                <a href="/jobs/{{ id }}">{{ title }}</a>
              </h5>
              <h6 class="card-subtitle my-1 text-body-secondary">
                {{ location }}
                •
                {{ salary }}
              </h6>
              <small class="card-text text-body-secondary">
                posted
                {{ posted }}
              </small>
            </div>
          </div>
          {{/jobs}}
        </div>

        <div class="offset-lg-2 col-lg-8">
          <table class="d-none d-md-table table table-striped table-bordered">
            <tr class="table-primary text-center">
              <th>Job Title</th>
              <th>Location</th>
              <th>Salary</th>
              <th>Posted On</th>
            </tr>
            {{#jobs}}
            <tr>
              <td>
                <a href="/jobs/{{ id }}">{{ title }}</a>
              </td>
              <td>{{ location }}</td>
              <td>{{ salary }}</td>
              <td>{{ posted }}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/jobs}}
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container col-xxl-10 py-5 px-4">
        <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis lh-1 mb-5">Projects</h2>
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide">
